  "title": "Sales Engineer (Electrical)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Engineering</strong> <strong>industry </strong>is seeking a <strong>Sales Engineer </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Sales Engineer (Electrical Products)</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> East (Nearest MRT: Tai Seng)</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, 8.30am to 5.30pm</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $4,800 + Quarterly Commission + Performance Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and expand key client accounts across key industrial sectors such as Oil and Gas, Energy, Life Sciences etc.</li>\n  <li>Manage the full sales process including client engagement, project estimates, proposal preparation, and order closure.</li>\n  <li>Provide technical consultation and support to clients for the sale of industrial electrical solutions and related products.</li>\n  <li>Meet or exceed assigned sales revenue and profitability targets.</li>\n  <li>Gather and analyze client technical needs while tracking market and competitive insights.</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain strong relationships with stakeholders at multiple levels within client organizations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum NITEC in Electrical Engineering or a related discipline.</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of B2B sales experience in a relevant industry.</li>\n  <li>Solid understanding of electrical products and applications.</li>\n  <li>Must hold a valid driver’s license and have own transport.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
